text: Emma Snerle (born 23 March 2001) is a Danish footballer who plays as a midfielder for Fortuna Hjørring and has appeared for the Denmark women's national team. ==Career== Snerle has been capped for the Denmark national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Danish women's footballers Category:Denmark women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Fortuna Hjørring players
